@startuml
title Docs frontend — Rocket smoke renderer pipeline (per fixed step)

skinparam linetype ortho

rectangle "Particle pool\n(2 400 GL / 800 2D)" as Pool

rectangle "emit()" as Emit
note bottom of Emit
  Boil phase only:
  squashed-disc emission
  around nozzle, vy ≥ 0
end note

rectangle "physicsStep()" as Phys
note bottom of Phys
  settle + drag + 3-frequency swirl
  ceiling clamp at startY − 2·s
  smoke killed at lift-off
end note

cloud "WebGL2 path\ninstanced quads\n+ domain-warped FBM shader" as GL
cloud "Canvas2D fallback\n3-stop radial gradients" as C2

frame "smoke pass\npremultiplied over" as P1
frame "hot pass\nadditive" as P2

Pool --> Emit : write head\n(ring buffer)
Emit --> Phys : updated state
Phys --> GL : useGL = true
Phys --> C2 : useGL = false

GL --> P1
GL --> P2
C2 --> P1
C2 --> P2

note right of GL
  pack instance buffers (positions × DPR)
  drawArraysInstanced × 2 passes
  uPass uniform routes particle type
end note

note right of C2
  iterate pool, draw radialGradient
  globalCompositeOperation per pass
end note

@enduml
